  49:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_exti.c ****     (#) Configure the EXTI line using HAL_EXTI_SetConfigLine().
  50:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Choose the interrupt line number by setting "Line" member from
  51:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_exti.c ****              EXTI_ConfigTypeDef structure.
