  55:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_exti.c ****              "Trigger" member from EXTI_ConfigTypeDef structure.
  56:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) For Exti lines linked to gpio, choose gpio port using "GPIOSel"
